				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2011/08/bgeeks11-epilogue-its-good-to-be-in-something-from-the-ground-floor/" title="Permalink to #BGeeks11 &#8211; Epilogue: It&#8217;s Good To Be In Something From the Ground Floor" rel="bookmark">#BGeeks11 &#8211; Epilogue: It&#8217;s Good To Be In Something From the Ground Floor</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2011-08-02T23:14:18+0000">Tuesday, August 2nd, 2011</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
<p> ”Lord, I’ve been thinking- spiritual friendship is at least half of the spiritual life!”  The Buddha replied: “Say not so, Ananda, say not so. Spiritual friendship is the whole of the spiritual life!” (Samyutta Nikaya, Verse 2) I&#8217;m still riding high from the Buddhist Geeks Conference over the weekend. I&#8217;ve already posted a daily summary (see [&hellip;]</p>
